ActFirst Nations Oil and Gas and Moneys Management Act
PrecisEnactment of the FIRST NATIONS OIL AND GAS AND MONEYS MANAGEMENT VOTING REGULATIONS which establish rules and procedures for conducting a vote within a First Nation community and the terms under which the Government of Canada will authorize them to manage their capital and revenue trust moneys and oil and gas resources.
